    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i don't think i'm adjusting them. i was just sitting there alone and it happened. and it's not just the temperature, the fridge hum is so specific, like it's almost a frequency. if someone actually wanted to use these things to monitor a house, how would they even do it? like, what kind of tech would they use to turn a thermostat or a fridge into a sensor?",
